            <!-- KineMaster Lite vs. KineMaster Pro -->
            <section id="comparison">
                <h2>KineMaster Lite vs. KineMaster Pro</h2>
                <p>KineMaster Lite is ideal for beginners and casual users due to its lightweight nature and easy-to-use interface. It offers essential editing tools without overwhelming the user. In contrast, KineMaster Pro is geared towards advanced users and professionals, providing a comprehensive suite of features, including advanced effects, higher-quality exports, and more customization options. While KineMaster Lite focuses on simplicity and efficiency, KineMaster Pro delivers extensive functionality for those requiring more robust editing capabilities.</p>
            </section>

